                <p class="small text-muted mb-2">R</p>
                <p class="text-muted small flex-grow-1">
                  An R wrapper around the birdnet Python package, providing convenient functions for running BirdNET and
                  handling results in R.
                </p>
                <a href="https://github.com/birdnet-team/birdnetR" class="stretched-link small" data-i18n="tools.viewOnGithub">
